                                    <h3 class="text-center">Battery Type and Size</h3>
                                    <p>Ensuring that you choose the correct battery type and size that is compatible with your truck's model is of utmost importance. To determine the appropriate battery specifications, it is recommended to refer to your vehicle's owner's manual or seek advice from a professional mechanic. This step will help guarantee a proper fit and optimal performance for your truck's battery.</p>
