                                    <h3 class="text-center">Battery Capacity</h3>
                                    <p>When selecting a truck battery, it's essential to consider its capacity, which is measured in ampere-hours (AH) and indicates the battery's power supply duration. Assessing the power requirements of your truck, including the number of electrical accessories it utilizes, will help determine the appropriate battery capacity. This consideration ensures that your truck has sufficient power to meet its electrical demands effectively.</p>
